nodes.text: Kean Ma'Sheavor was a male human officer of the Galactic Republic at the time of the Galactic War. During the Dread War, he was stationed on the moon Oricon's surface as a supply officer specializing in captured goods for Strike Team Oricon.

Kean Ma'Sheavor was first added to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic in Game Update 2.4: The Dread War. He serves as the Reputation Vendor for Strike Team Oricon, the Republic version of the reputation group on Oricon.
